subject: Empire State Building (NYC)
lead_paragraph: Thomas Dold of Germany and Suzy Walsham of Singapore repeated as winners of the Empire State Building Run-Up. In his fourth consecutive victory, Dold, 24, finished in 10 minutes 7 seconds. Walsham, 35, a native of Australia, earned her third consecutive victory in 13 minutes 27 seconds.
